nodes.text: Indra Ové (born September 27, 1967) is a British actress who portrays a First Order officer in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. Other roles of note include a New Orleans prostitute that Tom Cruise's Lestat interacts with in the 1994 film Interview with the Vampire, and roles in the British television series The World's Worst Witch, the British–German sci-fi co-production Space Island One and the British medical drama television series Holby City.
